# Alpaca API Credentials
# Get your Trading API keys from: https://app.alpaca.markets/paper/dashboard/overview
# For paper trading, use paper trading keys. For live trading, use live keys.

ALPACA_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
ALPACA_SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key-here

# Usage:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual API keys
# 3. Source the environment: source .env (or use direnv)
# 
# Note: Never commit your .env file with real credentials to the repository if contributing.
